text: Game Shakers is a Canadian television series created by Dan Schneider that aired on Nickelodeon from September 12, 2015 to June 8, 2019. The series stars Cree Cicchino, Madisyn Shipman, Benjamin "Lil' P-Nut" Flores, Jr., Thomas Kuc, and Kel Mitchell.The series was directed by Dan Schneider and Edgar Agayi. ==Broadcast== The series premiered on TVOKids Télémagino and Knowledge Network in Canada on October 6, 2015,and debuted on Nickelodeon channels in the United Kingdom and Ireland on November 2, 2015, and in Australia and New Zealand on February 8, 2016. ==References== Category:2010s American television series Category:Nickelodeon television series Category:2015 American television series debuts
